	Awed Jen    
	 London, March 14 (PTI): Jennifer Aniston is in awe of her Friends co-star Courteney Cox-Arquettes daughter Coco and tries to spend as much time with her as possible.      
	The actress is godmother to five-year-old Coco and spends her weekends with the child, Contactmusic has reported.      
	Coco calls me Nuna. I see her almost every weekend and shes really turning into such a lovely little girl. Shes sweet, funny and creative. We just sit there in awe of her, the 40-year-old said.     
	New Dustin    
	 London (PTI): After spending a lifetime in front of the camera, Dustin Hoffman is going behind it for the first time. The Oscar-winning actor is in the final stages of negotiations to direct his first film, featuring Maggie Smith, Albert Finney and Tom Courtenay, Daily Mail has reported online. Hoffman was in Los Angeles over the Oscar weekend, thrashing out last-minute details of a deal to direct Quartet, set in a retirement home for opera singers. The 72-year-old has been acting in movies for more than 40 years.     
	Emma split     
	 London(PTI): Emma Watson, who plays Hermione Granger in the Harry Potter films, has ended her two-year relationship with financier Jay Barrymore. The couple split after Watson, 19, grew close to Spanish musician and fellow student at Brown University Rafael Cebrian. The pair have been spending time together off late, Daily Mail has reported online.                                                                                                                                                      
